		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
		
		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="+2">Shadowknight Darkforge Armor</FONT><BR>
Zone : Najena<BR><BR>
<TABLE CELLSPACING = 0 CELLPADDING = 0 BORDER = 0>
<TR><TD><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="ariel"><B>Updated:</B> November 13th 1999</B><BR><BR>

There is an Undead Knight in Castle Mistmoore who will make Darkforge Armor, which can only be worn by Shadowknights, if you bring him the proper ingredients. The undead knight spawns in the room with the coffin in the graveyard (although he seems a rare spawn). Be aware that he will often get killed by other players, so you may just have to wait around from him to spawn. Decaying armor is found on Lizardman Crusaders in Cazic Thule, and is no drop lore, so you have to get it yourself. There may be a left and right component to each piece. The remaining pieces can be obtained in Najena (see below). <BR><BR> 

<B>In Castle Mistmoore:</B><BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=199">Darkforge Helm:</A> Decaying Helm, Decaying Visor and 2 Freeport Militia Helms (from Freeport guards) <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=198">Darkforge Breastplate:</A> Decaying Breastplate, Decaying Mail, and 2 enchanted bars of platinum <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=130">Darkforge Bracers:</A> Decaying Bracers and Minotaur Shackles (from the Minotaur Hero) <BR><BR>  

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=128">Darkforge Vambraces:</A> Decaying Vambraces and Qeynos Kite Shield (from Qeynos guards) <BR><BR>

<B>In Najena: (another Undead Shadowknight )</B><BR><BR>

<A HREF=" http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=129">Darkforge Gauntlets:</A> Decaying Gauntlets plus 1 bar
 of enchanted platinum.<BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=201">Darkforge Greaves:</A> Decaying Greaves (both right and left) plus 2 Melatite from Sol Mining Co. (Gnomes in Sol A)<BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=200"> Darkforge Boots:</A> Decaying Boots (both right and left) plus 2 Faerie Dust (Faerie Guards in Faydark).<BR><BR>

<B>NEW:</B> Click <A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/files/darkforge_armor.zip">HERE</A> to download a single page checklist for this quest that is in Word '97 format. A handy tool to help organize all the steps involved.<BR><BR>
</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
